## Known Issue: ColdClientLoader.ini Path Mismatch

> [!WARNING]
> `SteamUtils.writeColdClientIni()` uses `container.executablePath` for the exe path, 
> which may be empty for Steam games launched from Library. The generated path 
> `steamapps\common\gameName\<executablePath>` doesn't align with the A: drive mount path.
> This means the Goldberg emulator may not find the game exe via ColdClientLoader.ini,
> even though Wine launches the correct exe via winhandler.
